msgstr "Express-Button-Symbol"

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:214
msgid "Show icon on Express Payment button"
msgstr "Symbol auf Express-Zahlung-Button anzeigen"

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:217
msgid ""
"When enabled, the payment network icon is displayed alongside the button "
"label."
msgstr ""
"Wenn aktiviert, wird das Zahlungsnetzwerk-Symbol neben der Button-"
"Beschriftung angezeigt."

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:220
msgid "Icon Position"
msgstr "Symbol-Position"

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:223
msgid ""
"Controls where the icon appears relative to the button label. e.g. \"₿ Pay "
"with\" (left) or \"Pay with ₿\" (right)."
msgstr ""
"Steuert, wo das Symbol relativ zur Button-Beschriftung angezeigt wird. Z.B. "
"\"₿ Bezahlen mit\" (links) oder \"Bezahlen mit ₿\" (rechts)."

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:225
