msgstr "Nur für Administratoren anzeigen."

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:238
msgid ""
"If enabled, only administrators will see the payment method on Checkout page."
msgstr ""
"Wenn aktiviert, sehen nur Administratoren die Zahlungsart auf der Checkout-"
"Seite."

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:241
msgid "Debug"
msgstr "Debug"

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:242
msgid "Enable debugging messages"
msgstr "Debug-Meldungen aktivieren"

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:245
msgid "Debug logs will be saved to WooCommerce > Status > Logs."
msgstr ""
"Debug-Protokolle werden unter WooCommerce > Status > Protokolle gespeichert."

